description: Hold-ups with paperwork mean the "practical option" is to start next year, the health minister says.
title: Isle of Man coronavirus vaccinations 'delayed until January'
title_page: Isle of Man coronavirus vaccinations 'delayed until January' - BBC News
maintext: He said: "It is not sensible to start with so little margin in the immediate run up to Christmas Day, and we will not rush things during an already very busy period for our health services."
